snippet.title: Pete Davidson Tells Kanye West To STOP Calling Kim Kardashian His Wife...!?
snippet.description:
Don't you just hate it when love triangles happen in the real world? Oh, you don't hate it? Wow, you need to get new hobbies to enjoy then! Regardless, the celeb world is full of tales both famous and infamous in regards to the love triangles that have filled them up over the decades. And right now, there's one brewing that could literally set the celeb world on fire if things don't go the right way, we speak of course of what's happening between Kim Kardashian, Pete Davidson, and a now resurgent Kanye West. All three have made their intentions known, and this will get interesting...so we'll break it down for you! Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at what is going down with these three celebs who just so happen to have their eyes set on someone else in the triangle. Do you think that this might get ugly given that Kanye is usually up for doing just about anything to get what he wants? Do you think that Kim will have to go and make a statement soon to put rumors of her and Kanye getting back together to rest? What are Pete Davidson's options in this? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
